title: History Channel The Re Inventors Flying Car Xvid AC3
description:
With the advent and spread of airplanes and automobiles in the beginning of the 20th century an idea emerged that a marriage of the two would create the ultimate travel vehicle for the average person. Is this feasible or even possible to create a flying car the average person could afford? Join the Re-Inventors as they look at the options and even construct one to see if it would work.
